  "description": "From the manufacturer AmazonBasics 6-Piece Dinner Plate Set Bring an elegant sense of contemporary style to the kitchen and dining room with this everyday AmazonBasics plate set. A nice choice for family meals and casual gatherings, the set includes six 10.5' diameter dinner plates. Space Saving To save on space, the dinner plates can easily stack on top of each other for compact storage in a cupboard or hutch. Detail AB-grade porcelain; BPA-free; lightweight yet durable Elegant white finish Safe in your microwave, oven, freezer, and dishwasher Includes six 26.5 cm dinner plates Plates can withstand temperatures between 300 and -15 degrees (Celsius) High-Quality Porcelain for Everyday Use Made of AB-grade porcelain, the high-quality dinner plate set offers reliable strength and durability, as well as a lightweight design for easy handling. The porcelain set is also BPA-free, so there's no need to worry about BPA seeping into food like with some plastic dishes and containers. The porcelain set can be safely used in the freezer, microwave, and oven, though be careful, as the plates will get hot. The set of plates can withstand temperatures between 300 and -15 degrees (Celsius) What's more, the everyday plate set can go in the dishwasher, making cleanup a snap. Simple Style The sleek white design complements existing dinnerware pieces, table linen, and surrounding decor, making it a versatile household item. In The Box Six 26.5 cm dinner plates",
